{"word":"G2638 - καταλαμβάνω - katalambánō - kat-al-am-ban'-o - Apprehend","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταλαμβάνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">katalambánō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-al-am-ban'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Apprehend</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பிடி, பற்றிக்கொள்ளு, அகப்படு, அடை, பெறு, அறி"},{"paragraph":"1. to lay hold of, to obtain, attain to"},{"paragraph":"2. to seize upon, take possession of"},{"paragraph":"3. to detect, catch"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G1983 - ἐπισκοπέω - episkopéō - ep-ee-skop-eh'-o/1983\">G1983</a>; to <i>take eagerly</i>, that is, <i>seize</i>, <i>possess</i>, etc. (literally or figuratively): - apprehend, attain, come upon, comprehend, find, obtain, perceive, (over-) take.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1949/1949\">G1949</a>, <a href=\"#/G2638/2638\">G2638</a>, <a href=\"#/G2983/2983\">G2983</a>, <a href=\"#/G3335/3335\">G3335</a>, <a href=\"#/G3336/3336\">G3336</a>, <a href=\"#/G353/353\">G353</a>, <a href=\"#/G354/354\">G354</a>, <a href=\"#/G3880/3880\">G3880</a>, <a href=\"#/G423/423\">G423</a>, <a href=\"#/G4301/4301\">G4301</a>, <a href=\"#/G4355/4355\">G4355</a>, <a href=\"#/G4356/4356\">G4356</a>, <a href=\"#/G5274/5274\">G5274</a>"}]}